  "title": "Staff Nurse (Oncology / Chemotherapy) Locum / Perm opening available ! #HYT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Sector:</strong> Healthcare / Clinical Services<br /><strong>Employment Type:</strong></p><p><ul><li>Permanent (Clinic-Based)</li><li>3-Month Agency Contract</li></ul></p><p><strong>Working Hours:</strong></p><p><ul><li>Permanent role: Clinic staggered office hours</li><li>Contract role: 5 days, office hours</li></ul></p><p><strong>Compensation:</strong></p><p><ul><li>Permanent role: Salary negotiable based on experience</li><li>Contract role: $29 per hour</li></ul></p><h3><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></h3><p><ul><li>Provide safe and professional nursing care for oncology patients</li><li>Administer chemotherapy and support treatment plans</li><li>Monitor patient condition and respond to changes appropriately</li><li>Maintain accurate clinical documentation</li><li>Follow infection control and clinical safety standards</li><li>Work collaboratively with doctors and allied health teams</li></ul></p><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><p><ul><li>Registered Staff Nurse with valid licence</li><li>Oncology and chemotherapy training is mandatory<br /></li></ul><p>All qualified applicants, please click “ APPLY NOW”<br /></p><p>Or you may send in your resume to:</p><p>Whatsapp: <a href=\"https://wa.me/+6597430026\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://wa.me/+6597430026</a>  </p><p>Email : <a href=\"mailto:kimlow@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">kimlow@recruitexpress.com.sg</a><br /></p><p>Kimmy Low Yi Ting (Kim) | CEI Registration Number: R23112122</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd Company Reg. No. 199601303W | EA LICENCE Number: 99C4599</p></p>",
